<br>
Problems with this may be caused by being out of synch with the intended spawn.  Before turning in the medalion, hail him first and make sure he insists on responding only to official business. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udyllwindw.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DyllwinDW</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/20/01 1:52:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3440.topic&index=125>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Nathyn Illuminous/Locked Chest</span><hr size=1> I think the reason Nathyn tossed Valdonov outta town was because of what a &quot;Vampyre Volitalis&quot; is...<br>
