<br>
Do this:<br>
1) Hail Nathyn Illuminous - he should say something along the lines of &quot;I don't remember inviting you.. I am a busy man..&quot;<br>
<br>
2) Turn in your first badge.<br>
<br>
*The fix* 3) Hail Nathyn Illuminous - he will say nothing<br>
<br>
4) Who is Valdanov Zafeer?<br>
<br>
5) Quite some time?<br>
<br>
6) Captured vampyres<br>
<br>
